bll_nyc_rate <- bll_nyc %>% mutate(
    Borough = case_when(
      borough_id == 1 ~ "Bronx",
      borough_id == 2 ~ "Brooklyn",
      borough_id == 3 ~ "Manhattan",
      borough_id == 4 ~ "Queens",
      borough_id == 5 ~ "Staten Island")) %>% 
  rename(Year = time_period) %>%
  group_by(Year, Borough) %>%
  summarize("BLL > 5ug/DL" = bll_5/1000,
            "BLL > 10ug/DL" = bll_10/1000,
            "BLL > 15ug/DL" = bll_15/1000) %>%
  select(Borough, Year, "BLL > 5ug/DL", "BLL > 10ug/DL", "BLL > 15ug/DL")
